name: SourceInputSensorOffset
comment: calibration value for air inlet sensor

name: PollutionDetect
comment: unusual low brine temperaure at high air inlet temperature

name: HotSummer
comment: air inlet too hot to run compressor

name: DeiceTimeMax
comment: max. deicing time. By exceeding this value, message unsuccessful deicing is released

name: DeicePeriodMin
comment: Min. time between deicings. If time is shorter, something is wrong

name: DeltaTMax
comment: start defrost process when temperature difference between air and brine is above this setpoint

name: DeiceOnTemp
comment: above this air temperature ice is quite unusual

name: OnlyFanTemp
comment: above this air temperature, the defroster is not used for defrosting, only fan

name: DeiceWFanHyst
comment: remaining temperature difference to air inlet while fan defrosting

name: FanSpeedMax
comment: maximum allowed fan speed, set by look-up-table according to IDU power

name: NoiseReductionFactor
comment: noise reduction factor to reduce fan speed

name: CompActive
comment: compressor is running or pre or post running

name: CompDemand
comment: compressor wants to start or is running

name: SourceOK
comment: brine pressure is ok and pump is running

name: ODUReady
comment: start-up test of ODU was successful
